Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:04.12,default,,0,0,0,,Go on. Eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.12,0:00:05.96,default,,0,0,0,,The white sausage is great here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.04,0:00:10.96,default,,0,0,0,,How is it? It's delicious, isn't it? It's Dieter, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:16.72,default,,0,0,0,,If you don't eat, Dieter's going to eat it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.39,0:00:20.26,default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.73,0:00:24.73,default,,0,0,0,,It's safe here. Only regulars come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:29.82,default,,0,0,0,,If someone new came,\NOtto would throw them right out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.40,0:00:33.90,default,,0,0,0,,Because I only have people like you\Nhere, business does not improve.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.70,0:00:36.20,default,,0,0,0,,Who ordered the Spetzel?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.45,0:00:37.99,default,,0,0,0,,That was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.70,0:00:41.16,default,,0,0,0,,I've prepared a bed in the attic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.95,0:00:44.16,default,,0,0,0,,If you can stand the rats, you can rest there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.62,0:00:46.83,default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Otto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.59,0:00:51.63,default,,0,0,0,,He might seem a bit unsociable, but\Nhe's got a good side to him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:54.59,default,,0,0,0,,Eat! You can't go on an empty stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.13,0:00:57.89,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. You've even gone so\Nfar as to arrange a room for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.64,0:01:00.30,default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who should be thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.97,0:01:04.89,default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't saved me, I'd be in the morgue.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.69,0:01:09.56,default,,0,0,0,,I feel more alive eating this great food.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.19,0:01:11.23,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm so full.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.74,0:01:15.86,default,,0,0,0,,I've contacted Dr. Gillen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.45,0:01:19.32,default,,0,0,0,,He's relieved that we've found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.32,0:01:23.41,default,,0,0,0,,He left a message for you in a newspaper ad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.62,0:01:26.58,default,,0,0,0,,"Let's discuss our memories of cheating."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.21,0:01:28.25,default,,0,0,0,,You knew about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:29.25,default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.09,0:01:32.34,default,,0,0,0,,Then why didn't you contact him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.51,0:01:36.34,default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to draw him into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.76,0:01:40.85,default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:42.85,default,,0,0,0,,The thing we need the most is friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.64,0:01:48.60,default,,0,0,0,,So, you said that you were watching over me for some time?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:51.36,default,,0,0,0,,Because of the incident with Richard Braun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.02,0:01:52.86,default,,0,0,0,,Richard?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.57,0:01:58.45,default,,0,0,0,,When he was on the police force, he\Nshot a young serial murder suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.61,0:02:05.62,default,,0,0,0,,When I was reading that newspaper article,\NDieter saw the boy in the photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.50,0:02:10.58,default,,0,0,0,,He was in 511 Kinderheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:13.50,default,,0,0,0,,511 Kinderheim?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:16.13,default,,0,0,0,,An orphanage in East Berlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.13,0:02:17.13,default,,0,0,0,,A special one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.22,0:02:23.60,default,,0,0,0,,Dieter's foster parent was originally a teacher there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:26.85,default,,0,0,0,,Was there something about that orphanage?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.68,0:02:28.85,default,,0,0,0,,Johan was there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:34.27,default,,0,0,0,,So the boy that Richard shot and Johan\Nmight be connected somehow then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:35.90,default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:41.86,default,,0,0,0,,I came here because I wanted to investigate that\Nin more detail, but now Richard is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:46.33,default,,0,0,0,,At the cemetery, I saw you in front of his grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.83,0:02:54.13,default,,0,0,0,,It's as if Richard brought you to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:02:59.47,default,,0,0,0,,You've hung in there for so long by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:02.43,default,,0,0,0,,But now you're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:05.10,default,,0,0,0,,I will prove your innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.89,0:03:08.10,default,,0,0,0,,Johan is just in front of our eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.10,0:03:10.85,default,,0,0,0,,The photo... Huh? What happened to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:13.19,default,,0,0,0,,I must have left it in the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:17.11,default,,0,0,0,,I thought we'd know everything once\NI'd shown you Johan's picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:21.36,default,,0,0,0,,Probably, the man who came to kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:24.70,default,,0,0,0,,Was ordered to destroy it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:28.20,default,,0,0,0,,That man's name was Hesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.45,0:03:30.58,default,,0,0,0,,His wife had been coming for counseling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:36.84,default,,0,0,0,,I looked at his contact information and found\Nout there wasn't anyone named Hesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:40.67,default,,0,0,0,,Johan is right in front of our eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:44.30,default,,0,0,0,,And if he's so close, that means we'll meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:47.93,default,,0,0,0,,We'll meet him face to face...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:49.18,default,,0,0,0,,We'll meet Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:23.13,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,750)\pos(360,340)}In Broad Daylight
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.89,0:05:24.06,default,,0,0,0,,Tahlbach & Schubert AG...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:27.02,default,,0,0,0,,That company was the center of Schubert's financial world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.69,0:05:32.15,default,,0,0,0,,Schubert, who usually didn't appear\Nanywhere, began to show up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.03,0:05:37.95,default,,0,0,0,,At about this time of the morning, he used to inspect\Nthe companies that he was involved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.95,0:05:39.83,default,,0,0,0,,That's what Richard found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:47.88,default,,0,0,0,,Not only this company, but all of his financial groups\Ncame here and greatly improved their earnings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.50,0:05:51.88,default,,0,0,0,,Ever since that certain boy became his assistant, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:55.13,default,,0,0,0,,Here he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:05.48,default,,0,0,0,,The one in the wheelchair is Schubert.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:08.10,default,,0,0,0,,The one pushing him is Karl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:09.98,default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:34.55,default,,0,0,0,,Well, is it him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:38.64,default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.05,0:06:40.55,default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:42.81,default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:49.19,default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time I've seen him in broad daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:53.94,default,,0,0,0,,That's right. We'll bring everything into broad daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.82,0:06:56.70,default,,0,0,0,,It has to be now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:06:58.24,default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.24,0:07:00.45,default,,0,0,0,,We have to prove your innocence now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:05.37,default,,0,0,0,,But for now, we should go hide in Otto's attic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:08.96,default,,0,0,0,,We'll clear your name soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:15.26,default,,0,0,0,,Richard's file is around here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:18.09,default,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:21.14,default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I brought this home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.56,0:07:28.39,default,,0,0,0,,We're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.81,0:07:31.44,default,,0,0,0,,We're almost there, Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:35.23,default,,0,0,0,,Your revenge will be complete when\Nwe find one more person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:37.69,default,,0,0,0,,We're right on Johan's heels.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.57,0:07:42.07,default,,0,0,0,,I've found Dr. Tenma, a key witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.99,0:07:43.74,default,,0,0,0,,All that's left is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:49.12,default,,0,0,0,,We need to find a witness from\Nthe night of Richard's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:50.58,default,,0,0,0,,There's got to be one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.58,0:07:55.71,default,,0,0,0,,We just need someone to verify that Johan\Nwas the one with Richard that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:08:01.59,default,,0,0,0,,If we can't do that, there's still the student, Farhen, who\Nclaimed to be Schubert's son, and committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.72,0:08:07.39,default,,0,0,0,,If Johan was the young boy who went\Nwith him to see the prostitute,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:10.94,default,,0,0,0,,and if we could find that prostitute, we'd be able to prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:12.90,default,,0,0,0,,That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.73,0:08:18.03,default,,0,0,0,,If we find the people who said they were Johan's parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.03,0:08:19.57,default,,0,0,0,,we might be able to find out exactly who Johan is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:23.82,default,,0,0,0,,After all, I found the grave of Johan Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:27.95,default,,0,0,0,,We've got Johan right where we want him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:34.63,default,,0,0,0,,Say, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:38.26,default,,0,0,0,,When I look at you, you remind me of Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:44.22,default,,0,0,0,,It looks like you're fighting for all the justice in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.89,0:08:47.31,default,,0,0,0,,but you're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:48.27,default,,0,0,0,,Dieter is with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:51.14,default,,0,0,0,,So is Dr. Gillen, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:52.23,default,,0,0,0,,And so am I!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.69,0:08:57.19,default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Sleep well tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.36,0:09:06.41,default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to drag him into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:10.12,default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.75,0:09:15.42,default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time I've seen him in broad daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.13,0:09:19.13,default,,0,0,0,,It has to be now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.34,0:09:25.05,default,,0,0,0,,You're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:26.47,default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:29.22,default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.69,0:09:42.90,default,,0,0,0,,Hello, this is Reichwine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:45.16,default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, it's Gillen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:50.08,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, actually, I was just about to call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:52.91,default,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:54.96,default,,0,0,0,,Where's Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:57.83,default,,0,0,0,,He's at the hideout I mentioned before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.79,0:10:01.05,default,,0,0,0,,Tell him not to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:03.22,default,,0,0,0,,Something's wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:04.88,default,,0,0,0,,I felt there was something wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:13.14,default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma isn't chasing after Johan to clear his name...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.64,0:10:17.23,default,,0,0,0,,I was worried about that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:35.08,default,,0,0,0,,Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:41.63,default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:45.88,default,,0,0,0,,Tenma told me to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:48.89,default,,0,0,0,,Where's Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.35,0:10:51.10,default,,0,0,0,,He left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:52.10,default,,0,0,0,,Where d he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.89,0:10:54.14,default,,0,0,0,,He's going to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:10:55.02,default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:10:57.64,default,,0,0,0,,Tenma's going to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.98,0:11:03.65,default,,0,0,0,,Stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.94,0:11:07.61,default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Reichwine, stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.45,0:11:08.82,default,,0,0,0,,Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.62,0:11:11.12,default,,0,0,0,,He's going to become a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:40.16,default,,0,0,0,,Let's quit here for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.91,0:11:43.46,default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that. Please listen to me, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:46.29,default,,0,0,0,,It gets interesting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:50.25,default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to take your time telling me the next part.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:54.68,default,,0,0,0,,The third woman I killed was the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.80,0:11:56.97,default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:12:00.51,default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.52,0:12:04.60,default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea what her voice\Nsounded like as I strangled her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:07.94,default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Doctor. Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.94,0:12:09.73,default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, that woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.95,0:12:18.99,default,,0,0,0,,Where did you go, Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.58,0:12:24.37,default,,0,0,0,,So, we finally meet, Dr. Gillen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:27.33,default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.42,0:12:31.42,default,,0,0,0,,I'm Lunge from the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:35.26,default,,0,0,0,,I've heard the rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.01,0:12:41.64,default,,0,0,0,,Many of my research subjects were arrested by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.98,0:12:47.19,default,,0,0,0,,I read your book as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.98,0:12:48.90,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.94,0:12:51.44,default,,0,0,0,,It's a great book.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.28,0:12:54.44,default,,0,0,0,,"A Summary of Abnormal Criminal Psychology."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.45,0:13:00.87,default,,0,0,0,,There are no other books that go\Nso deep into the criminal mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.74,0:13:09.00,default,,0,0,0,,Especially the 3rd Chapter, pages 262 to 294 on Heinz Kaul.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:15.26,default,,0,0,0,,I had a deep interest in the discussion\Nthat claimed that the trauma he
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.26,0:13:17.26,default,,0,0,0,,experienced at a young age led him to crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:23.64,default,,0,0,0,,How detailed. I'm honored you read it so thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.52,0:13:29.44,default,,0,0,0,,My method of investigation is to\Ndive into a criminal's heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.44,0:13:33.61,default,,0,0,0,,and walk through what he would think and do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:37.11,default,,0,0,0,,You have a lot of experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.11,0:13:39.66,default,,0,0,0,,If you have some time, I'd love to talk with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:44.95,default,,0,0,0,,Since we both don't have much free time, let me ask one thing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:49.16,default,,0,0,0,,You've been in Munich a lot lately, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:51.67,default,,0,0,0,,And what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.34,0:13:55.75,default,,0,0,0,,Please sit.  It won't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.97,0:14:02.76,default,,0,0,0,,You met with Dr. Reichwine, a psychologist, there
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:03.39,default,,0,0,0,,just the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.14,0:14:07.18,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he was a great teacher I had in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.64,0:14:09.31,default,,0,0,0,,At Dusseldorf University, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:10.60,default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.65,0:14:14.11,default,,0,0,0,,There was a great brain surgeon that graduated from
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:17.86,default,,0,0,0,,Dusseldorf University at around\Nthe same time as you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.65,0:14:20.86,default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:22.45,default,,0,0,0,,Did you meet him,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.28,0:14:24.32,default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:27.33,default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.91,0:14:30.41,default,,0,0,0,,"Let's discuss our memories of cheating." --Rudi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.29,0:14:38.46,default,,0,0,0,,From May 1st until May 22nd, you printed this three\Nline ad in all the major newspapers in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.59,0:14:41.34,default,,0,0,0,,That's quite surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:49.10,default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that such good students like you\Nand Dr. Tenma were cheating in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.23,0:14:52.39,default,,0,0,0,,Great things, aren't they? True friends, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.02,0:14:57.19,default,,0,0,0,,We weren't really friends back in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:14:59.74,default,,0,0,0,,Last year in May, in Oder Park...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.82,0:15:07.87,default,,0,0,0,,With your cooperation, the Velbert police were just\Nabout to arrest Dr. Tenma, but he got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:11.37,default,,0,0,0,,That was because the bug I was wearing broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:14.88,default,,0,0,0,,I think you helped him escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:20.46,default,,0,0,0,,He, Dr. Tenma, is innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.09,0:15:24.89,default,,0,0,0,,I want you to listen with an open mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.72,0:15:30.60,default,,0,0,0,,The three murders at Eisler Memorial\NHospital in Dusseldorf,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:33.64,default,,0,0,0,,the murder of the patient in the building\Nthat was under construction,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.65,0:15:35.98,default,,0,0,0,,the murder at Heidelberg,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:38.65,default,,0,0,0,,the murders of the middle-aged couples across\Nthe nation were not committed by Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.53,0:15:47.37,default,,0,0,0,,That's my opinion, as an expert in criminal psychology,\Nfrom my face to face meeting with Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:49.62,default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:51.50,default,,0,0,0,,Then, where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:54.71,default,,0,0,0,,He's gone somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:15:56.88,default,,0,0,0,,Why is he running?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.67,0:15:59.55,default,,0,0,0,,If he's innocent, why is he running?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:00.71,default,,0,0,0,,He's not running.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.63,0:16:05.97,default,,0,0,0,,Why did he leave without telling\Nyou? You're his friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.35,0:16:13.68,default,,0,0,0,,I have proof that he's not the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.40,0:16:16.69,default,,0,0,0,,Take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.69,0:16:22.94,default,,0,0,0,,All of the case's information has been\Ngathered and analyzed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.97,0:16:51.18,default,,0,0,0,,It must have been quite a lot of trouble to put this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:56.31,default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:16:57.31,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:17:03.82,default,,0,0,0,,The death of Farhen, the man who\Npretended to be Schubert's son,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.82,0:17:07.82,default,,0,0,0,,the death of the former police officer investigating\Nthe case, Richard Braun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.45,0:17:12.33,default,,0,0,0,,The suspicion about Schubert having an illegitimate son...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.41,0:17:16.75,default,,0,0,0,,The one in the center of it all is that young boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.75,0:17:21.29,default,,0,0,0,,and that boy's name is the same as the name\Nof the real killer that Tenma spoke about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:23.71,default,,0,0,0,,Johan Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.88,0:17:30.59,default,,0,0,0,,There is a person with the same\Nfirst and last name in Bruntal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:38.56,default,,0,0,0,,After the death of Richard Braun, someone\Nbegan to target Dr. Reichwine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.69,0:17:41.15,default,,0,0,0,,I understand quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.78,0:17:47.53,default,,0,0,0,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:52.32,default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to prove that all those things are related.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.04,0:17:58.21,default,,0,0,0,,And because he knew that fact the best, Tenma left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.17,0:18:01.33,default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:11.59,default,,0,0,0,,Those hand movements...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.52,0:18:16.93,default,,0,0,0,,Don't pay any attention to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:19.89,default,,0,0,0,,It's something I use to help me remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.77,0:18:27.03,default,,0,0,0,,A psychologist like me would say that it's the physical\Nrepresentation of the uncertainty in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.15,0:18:29.95,default,,0,0,0,,I'm the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.95,0:18:36.33,default,,0,0,0,,Instead of my hands, I play with this cassette recorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.12,0:18:43.83,default,,0,0,0,,The information recorded in your hand\Nmovements is by nature, subjective.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,0:18:48.55,default,,0,0,0,,That's how you've done your work\Nfor a long time now, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.26,0:18:50.63,default,,0,0,0,,Your hand's memories are correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.30,0:18:54.01,default,,0,0,0,,Your decisions were never mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.64,0:18:59.73,default,,0,0,0,,What are your hobbies?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.73,0:19:01.64,default,,0,0,0,,Do you live only for your work?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:04.10,default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever made a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:07.86,default,,0,0,0,,Are you horribly afraid of making a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.36,0:19:12.36,default,,0,0,0,,To you, Tenma must be the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:15.70,default,,0,0,0,,If he's not, your identity will be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:19.75,default,,0,0,0,,Look at the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.83,0:19:22.87,default,,0,0,0,,This is a photo of Johan Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.38,0:19:29.50,default,,0,0,0,,Can you prove that everything is just Tenma's lies?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.72,0:19:39.39,default,,0,0,0,,This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.73,0:19:42.35,default,,0,0,0,,Where is this young man now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:44.69,default,,0,0,0,,He's a student at Munich University.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.40,0:19:47.90,default,,0,0,0,,He's Schubert's secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.03,0:19:53.15,default,,0,0,0,,Can I have this photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.74,0:19:59.20,default,,0,0,0,,This is police business from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:05.87,default,,0,0,0,,I might have made a terrible mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.17,0:20:08.88,default,,0,0,0,,Where is Dr. Tenma now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.84,0:20:14.01,default,,0,0,0,,He should be in Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:34.40,default,,0,0,0,,It's Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.28,0:20:36.91,default,,0,0,0,,Send a message to the Munich Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.99,0:20:39.37,default,,0,0,0,,This is a request for emergency police officer deployment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.54,0:20:43.79,default,,0,0,0,,Tenma is in Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.55,0:20:53.46,default,,0,0,0,,A sniper rifle?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:57.22,default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.68,0:21:01.93,default,,0,0,0,,You should have gotten a call from\Na Mr. Heitmeyer in Fussen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:07.31,default,,0,0,0,,It'll be an advanced payment of 10,000 Marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.15,0:21:09.94,default,,0,0,0,,I've got it right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.36,0:21:19.41,default,,0,0,0,,Your order will be a bit hard to get ready\Nfor you, so you'll have to give me a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.41,0:21:22.33,default,,0,0,0,,You better toughen up before then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.91,0:21:28.33,default,,0,0,0,,If you pay a heap of money for something you can't use,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.01,0:21:34.88,default,,0,0,0,,On to the next item of news...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.88,0:21:42.35,default,,0,0,0,,The reception party for next week's Munich Electronics\NFair was held today by the Chamber of Commerce,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.35,0:21:46.52,default,,0,0,0,,and was attended by many leaders of the financial world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.31,0:21:50.69,default,,0,0,0,,The News Media Network, which is involved with the EU,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.69,0:21:52.86,default,,0,0,0,,is now supported by Bayern's industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.86,0:21:55.53,default,,0,0,0,,This will be a large-scale convention as never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.20,0:22:03.24,default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, at this reception a man who has not\Nbeen seen in public for the past twenty years,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.24,0:22:07.37,default,,0,0,0,,Harts Georg Schubert, attended and\Nreceived a unanimous welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.12,0:22:15.71,default,,0,0,0,,Although Schubert was in a wheelchair, he looked healthy and had great appeal with the financial leaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.99,0:23:53.49,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(360,340)}Sanctuary

